{"tid":1737294,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"林夕斥香港掌權人破壞法治","createTime":"2019-11-19T02:23:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-19T15:16:12.000Z","uid":25558,"like":74,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"f97023363576a4c9ddae267e24f95a63a0504cea","tid":1737294,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T02:23:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20191119/20808898\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20191119%2F20808898&d=uyJPOiOY0yV7leae1MMhfCZO8jd1M6XCUNMtuDfdPZA%3D&h=73e371cb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20191119%2F20808898&h=a153f178\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20191119/20808898</a><br />\n<br />\n林夕斥香港掌權人破壞法治<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20191119/large/1574083541_6718.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20191119%2Flarge%2F1574083541_6718.jpg&h=56fb220c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n林夕以國語帶領現場觀眾一起叫「香港加油」口號。台灣蘋果新聞網<br />\n<br />\n台灣「守民主護台灣大聯盟」前晚於台北自由廣場舉行「撐香港，要自由音樂會」，眾台灣樂隊出席之外，早前與滅火器樂團合作、推出支持香港抗爭歌曲《雙城記》的林夕，以黑衫黑褲打扮上台，他以國語叫出「香港加油」口號，然後他說『香港加油』這四個字，在香港已經成為一種罪，戴口罩也已經成為一種罪。他指更荒謬的是：「年輕是罪、穿上黑衣是罪，就連買雞蛋沒有收據也是罪。」林夕認為縱使示威者有破壞行為，但破壞法治是掌權的人，而且只有一個方法：「是執法不公，執法偏頗。」<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：藝人鬧理大校長呼喚學生<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20191119/large/1574083540_43c0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20191119%2Flarge%2F1574083540_43c0.jpg&h=55ab9077&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n台灣「守民主護台灣大聯盟」前晚在台北舉行「撐香港，要自由音樂會」，參與的包括朱頭皮蕭福德樂團。台灣蘋果新聞網<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20191119/large/1574083540_c1e0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20191119%2Flarge%2F1574083540_c1e0.jpg&h=73c1f167&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n香港遺城青年在台上聲援「光復香港 時代革命」。台灣蘋果新聞網<br />\n<br />\n林夕又激氣地表示，有旁觀者對年輕人抗爭會問：「這樣有用嗎？」林夕指：「有用沒用我們都不知道，我們做人有用嗎？做人終究一死，那就不做人？」當林夕提到周梓樂同學時，他特別感慨，指在周同學離世前幾天，他要寫韓國電影《1987：黎明來到的那一天》片尾曲的歌詞，他哭到電腦螢幕要放大二百倍才看到自己寫甚麼。林夕其後以死守理大的同學說的一句「我們不是因為認為有希望才堅持下去，我們相信堅持下去才有希望。」來鼓勵大家。<br />\n<br />\n撰文：翁可人 <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n導演鄧卓儒疑被補<br />\n<br />\n藝人鬧理大校長呼喚學生<br />\n導演鄧卓儒疑被補<br />\n校友邵仲衡梁芷珊籲救學生鄭敬基理大外食催淚彈「好擔心年輕人性命」"},{"pid":"8c3f7313a4ddd243352f5600c45dd4eaa41fe266","tid":1737294,"uid":104804,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T02:24:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n請受小弟一拜"},{"pid":"82f02f971530b7084af67c0287664f55d9daaf35","tid":1737294,"uid":25558,"like":36,"dislike":1,"score":35,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T02:25:57.000Z","msg":"有旁觀者對年輕人抗爭會問：「這樣有用嗎？」林夕指：「有用沒用我們都不知道，我們做人有用嗎？做人終究一死，那就不做人？」"},{"pid":"8aab0c93036cd72602ccd7457449ae209205311d","tid":1737294,"uid":124180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T02:28:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb33c165575f3a4cd657b262cfd108817e6716cb","tid":1737294,"uid":285165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T02:55:07.000Z","msg":"夕爺<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1030ba2790c2c22aee01389c2c4994